title: Custom emojis for the discord server
body:
Frens,

Allow me to borrow the words of world-renowned chef and gourmet, @BlockEnthusiast:

"What kinda self respecting discord doesn't have an emoji theme. All the newcomers will get scared away by how far they must scroll to react"

We must fix this terrible situation and cook some delicious Discord server boosting sauce (Moonato sauce 90%, ygmi water 5%, fine lambo extract 2%, vinegar, salt) for our beloved $PASTA discord.

Vote yes if you agree to allocate a mere 9.99$/month budget worth of $PASTA from the foodbank so that we can pimp up our kitchen with a level 1 nitro boost (https://support.discord.com/hc/en-us/articles/360028038352-Server-Boosting)

Vote no if you're a jabroni

--------------

Minimum Quorum: More than 15% of circulating supply must participate for this proposal to Pass. 

Passing Threshold: More than 50% of voting tokens must vote FOR for the proposal to Pass.
